        <Parent_String>Yersinia (genus) [300410397], Enterobacteriaceae (family) [300410398], Enterobacteriales (order) [300410399], Gammaproteobacteria (class) [300410400], Proteobacteria (phylum) [300410401], Bacteria (domain) [300265675], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
